# Prohibited Content

**Never** add the following (or anything similar) to:
- Git commit messages
- Code, comments, or documentation
- Any other project files or artifacts

- `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>`
- Any Co-authored-by or attribution line referring to Cursor / cursoragent

If the agent or editor suggests adding such lines (e.g. in a commit message), remove them before committing or saving.
